OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1784215104
OL,3,CPolice searching for 19-year-old
OL,4,Ckayaker reported missing off coast
OL,6,FPolice believe a man who is reported
OL,7,Fto have gone into the sea off the
OL,8,Fcoast of Northumberland has died.
OL,10,FNorthumbria Police received a report
OL,11,Fvia HM Coastguard on Tuesday just
OL,12,Fafter 9.15pm of a man being in the
OL,13,Fwater near Boulmer.
OL,15,FIt was reported that a kayak with two
OL,16,Fmen capsized, with one of them being
OL,17,Fable to swim to a buoy before being
OL,18,Frescued.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
