PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1784215104
OL,3,CPolice searching for 19-year-old
OL,4,Ckayaker reported missing off coast
OL,6,FSearches to locate and find the second
OL,7,Fman, aged 19, were immediately
OL,8,Flaunched and are being supported by
OL,9,Fspecialist officers.
OL,11,FThe efforts remain ongoing, but police
OL,12,Fnow believe the man will have died.
OL,14,FChief Inspector Jon Caisley, of
OL,15,FNorthumbria Police, said: "This is a
OL,16,Fvery tragic incident, and our thoughts
OL,17,Fare with the man's loved ones as this
OL,18,Ftime.
OL,26,@wD@[OU
