FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1784215104
OL,3,CPolice searching for 19-year-old
OL,4,Ckayaker reported missing off coast
OL,6,F"We will continue to support them in
OL,7,Fany way that we can, and would ask
OL,8,Fthat their privacy is respected.
OL,10,F"Searches continue but due to
OL,11,Fchallenging circumstances, we are not
OL,12,Fable to provide any timescales around
OL,13,Four efforts to recover the man.
OL,15,F"We would like to thank our colleagues
OL,16,Fat HM Coastguard and all of our
OL,17,Fpartners for their continued support."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOUyD@fO]
