OL,3,CPolice searching for 19-year-old
OL,4,Ckayaker reported missing off coast
OL,6,FPolice have asked members of the
OL,7,Fpublic not to attend the scene for
OL,8,Ftheir own safety and to allow trained
OL,9,Fprofessionals to continue their
OL,10,Fefforts.
